#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:5
msgid "Broad Crawls"
msgstr "广泛的爪子"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:7
msgid ""
"Scrapy defaults are optimized for crawling specific sites. These sites are "
"often handled by a single Scrapy spider, although this is not necessary or "
"required (for example, there are generic spiders that handle any given site "
"thrown at them)."
msgstr ""
"扫描默认值被优化用于覆盖特定站点。 这些场址往往由一个单一的废料喷洒器处理，但"
"没有必要或要求这样做（例如）。 那里有通用的喷雾器，处理任何向他们投掷的网"
"站)。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:12
msgid ""
"In addition to this \"focused crawl\", there is another common type of "
"crawling which covers a large (potentially unlimited) number of domains, and "
"is only limited by time or other arbitrary constraint, rather than stopping "
"when the domain was crawled to completion or when there are no more requests "
"to perform. These are called \"broad crawls\" and is the typical crawlers "
"employed by search engines."
msgstr ""
"除了这种“焦点角料”之外，还有另一种常见的覆盖大量（可能是无限制的）域。 而且只"
"受时间或其他任意限制， 而不是停止当域被夷为平地或没有更多的请求执行的时候。 "
"这些都叫做“大型箱子”，是搜索引擎使用的典型箱子。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:19
msgid "These are some common properties often found in broad crawls:"
msgstr "这些是一些常见的特性，常常出现在广泛的爪子里："

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:21
msgid ""
"they crawl many domains (often, unbounded) instead of a specific set of sites"
msgstr "他们捕捉了许多域名(常常是未弹出的) 而不是特定的站点。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:23
msgid ""
"they don't necessarily crawl domains to completion, because it would be "
"impractical (or impossible) to do so, and instead limit the crawl by time or "
"number of pages crawled"
msgstr ""
"它们不一定需要完成的域名，因为这样做是不切实际的(或不可能的)。 而是按时间或被"
"夷为平地的页数限制crawl"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:27
msgid ""
"they are simpler in logic (as opposed to very complex spiders with many "
"extraction rules) because data is often post-processed in a separate stage"
msgstr ""
"它们在逻辑上比较简单(而不是具有许多提取规则的非常复杂的拼写器)，因为数据往往"
"是在一个单独的阶段后处理的。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:30
msgid ""
"they crawl many domains concurrently, which allows them to achieve faster "
"crawl speeds by not being limited by any particular site constraint (each "
"site is crawled slowly to respect politeness, but many sites are crawled in "
"parallel)"
msgstr ""
"它们同时捕捉许多域名， 允许他们通过不受任何特定站点约束的限制来实现更快的 "
"crawl 速度(每个站点都会慢慢地被压缩到尊重政治性的状态) 但许多站点平行被夷为平"
"地)"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:35
msgid ""
"As said above, Scrapy default settings are optimized for focused crawls, not "
"broad crawls. However, due to its asynchronous architecture, Scrapy is very "
"well suited for performing fast broad crawls. This page summarizes some "
"things you need to keep in mind when using Scrapy for doing broad crawls, "
"along with concrete suggestions of Scrapy settings to tune in order to "
"achieve an efficient broad crawl."
msgstr ""
"如上文所述，精选电缆的默认设置是优化的，而不是宽泛的 crawl。 然而，由于其异步"
"结构，因此废料非常适合于进行快速宽阔的爪哇。 本页概述了在使用Scrapy进行广泛的"
"crawls时你需要记住的一些事情， 连同对废品设置的具体建议进行调整以便实现一种有"
"效率的宽阔箱子。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:47
msgid "Increase concurrency"
msgstr "增加同义性"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:49
msgid ""
"Concurrency is the number of requests that are processed in parallel. There "
"is a global limit (:setting:`CONCURRENT_REQUESTS`) and an additional limit "
"that can be set per domain (:setting:`CONCURRENT_REQUESTS_PER_DOMAIN`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:53
msgid ""
"The default global concurrency limit in Scrapy is not suitable for crawling "
"many different domains in parallel, so you will want to increase it. How "
"much to increase it will depend on how much CPU and memory your crawler will "
"have available."
msgstr ""
"废料中默认的全局同义词限制不适合平行翻转许多不同域名，所以你会想要增加它。 增"
"加多少将取决于您的 CPU 和内存的数量。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:58
msgid "A good starting point is ``100``:"
msgstr "一个很好的起点是 ``100`` ："

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:60
msgid "CONCURRENT_REQUESTS = 100"
msgstr "CONCRENT_REQUESTS = 100"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:64
msgid ""
"But the best way to find out is by doing some trials and identifying at what "
"concurrency your Scrapy process gets CPU bounded. For optimum performance, "
"you should pick a concurrency where CPU usage is at 80-90%."
msgstr ""
"但是找到问题的最佳途径是进行一些试验，并且确定你的废料处理程序有何同义词使得"
"CPU拥抱。 为了最佳性能，您应该选择一个 CPU 使用率为80%至90%的同系物。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:68
msgid ""
"Increasing concurrency also increases memory usage. If memory usage is a "
"concern, you might need to lower your global concurrency limit accordingly."
msgstr ""
"同时增加内存使用量也会增加内存使用量。如果内存使用令人担忧，您可能需要相应地"
"降低全局内币种限制。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:73
msgid "Increase Twisted IO thread pool maximum size"
msgstr "增加扭曲的 IO 线程池最大尺寸"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:75
msgid ""
"Currently Scrapy does DNS resolution in a blocking way with usage of thread "
"pool. With higher concurrency levels the crawling could be slow or even fail "
"hitting DNS resolver timeouts. Possible solution to increase the number of "
"threads handling DNS queries. The DNS queue will be processed faster "
"speeding up establishing of connection and crawling overall."
msgstr ""
"当前Scrapy 使用 DNS 解析以阻塞方式使用线程池。 由于同货币水平较高，卷轴可能较"
"慢，甚至击中DNS解析器超时。 增加处理DNS查询线程数的可能解决方案。 DNS队列将会"
"更快地处理连接加速和整流加速。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:81
msgid "To increase maximum thread pool size use:"
msgstr "要增加最大线程池大小，请使用："

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:83
msgid "REACTOR_THREADPOOL_MAXSIZE = 20"
msgstr "REACTOR_THREADPOOL_MAXSIZE = 20"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:88
msgid "Setup your own DNS"
msgstr "设置您自己的 DNS"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:90
msgid ""
"If you have multiple crawling processes and single central DNS, it can act "
"like DoS attack on the DNS server resulting to slow down of entire network "
"or even blocking your machines. To avoid this setup your own DNS server with "
"local cache and upstream to some large DNS like OpenDNS or Verizon."
msgstr ""
"如果你有多个卷轴过程和单个中央DNS, 它可以像DoS一样攻击DNS服务器，导致整个网络"
"减速，甚至阻挡您的机器。 为了避免这种设置，您自己的DNS服务器使用本地缓存和上"
"游流到一些大的DNS，如OpenDNS或Verizon。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:96
msgid "Reduce log level"
msgstr "降低日志级别"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:98
msgid ""
"When doing broad crawls you are often only interested in the crawl rates you "
"get and any errors found. These stats are reported by Scrapy when using the "
"``INFO`` log level. In order to save CPU (and log storage requirements) you "
"should not use ``DEBUG`` log level when performing large broad crawls in "
"production. Using ``DEBUG`` level when developing your (broad) crawler may "
"be fine though."
msgstr ""
"当你进行广泛的crawl时，你常常只关心你得到的crawl率和发现的任何错误。 当使用 "
"``INFO`` 日志时，这些统计数据由Scrapy 报告。 为了保存 CPU (和日志存储要求)，"
"你不应该在生产中执行大型笼子时使用 ``DEBUG`` 日志。 使用 ``DEBUG`` 来开发你"
"的 (broad) crawler 可能是很好的。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:105
msgid "To set the log level use:"
msgstr "要设置日志级别，请使用："

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:107
msgid "LOG_LEVEL = \"INFO\""
msgstr "LOG_LEVEL = “信息”"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:112
msgid "Disable cookies"
msgstr "禁用 cookie"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:114
msgid ""
"Disable cookies unless you *really* need. Cookies are often not needed when "
"doing broad crawls (search engine crawlers ignore them), and they improve "
"performance by saving some CPU cycles and reducing the memory footprint of "
"your Scrapy crawler."
msgstr ""
"禁用cookie，除非您*实际*需要。 在进行广泛的龙卷风时往往不需要cookie (搜索引擎"
"对它们置之不理)， 并通过保存一些CPU循环和减少废钢的内存足迹来提高性能。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:119
msgid "To disable cookies use:"
msgstr "要禁用 cookie 使用："

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:121
msgid "COOKIES_ENABLED = False"
msgstr "COOKIES_ENABLED = False"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:126
msgid "Disable retries"
msgstr "禁用重试"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:128
msgid ""
"Retrying failed HTTP requests can slow down the crawls substantially, "
"especially when sites causes are very slow (or fail) to respond, thus "
"causing a timeout error which gets retried many times, unnecessarily, "
"preventing crawler capacity to be reused for other domains."
msgstr ""
"重试失败的 HTTP 请求可能会大大减慢计时速度，尤其是当站点响应非常慢(或失败)"
"时， 因此导致超时错误，多次尝试不必要地阻止了 crawler 的容量用于其他域。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:133
msgid "To disable retries use:"
msgstr "要禁用重试使用："

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:135
msgid "RETRY_ENABLED = False"
msgstr "RETRY_ENABLED = False"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:140
msgid "Reduce download timeout"
msgstr "减少下载超时"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:142
msgid ""
"Unless you are crawling from a very slow connection (which shouldn't be the "
"case for broad crawls) reduce the download timeout so that stuck requests "
"are discarded quickly and free up capacity to process the next ones."
msgstr ""
"除非你从非常缓慢的连接中抓住(这种情况不应该是广泛的 crawls)，否则下载超时将会"
"减少，以便迅速丢弃被卡住的请求，并释放处理下一个请求的能力。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:146
msgid "To reduce the download timeout use:"
msgstr "为了减少下载超时使用："

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:148
msgid "DOWNLOAD_TIMEOUT = 15"
msgstr "下载_TIMEOUT = 15"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:153
msgid "Disable redirects"
msgstr "禁用重定向"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:155
msgid ""
"Consider disabling redirects, unless you are interested in following them. "
"When doing broad crawls it's common to save redirects and resolve them when "
"revisiting the site at a later crawl. This also help to keep the number of "
"request constant per crawl batch, otherwise redirect loops may cause the "
"crawler to dedicate too many resources on any specific domain."
msgstr ""
"考虑禁用重定向，除非您有兴趣关注它们。 当执行广泛的板条箱时，通常是在稍后的板"
"条箱中重新定向和解析它们。 这也有助于保持每个crawl批量的请求数量不变， 否则，"
"重定向循环可能会导致爬行者将太多资源用于任何特定领域。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:161
msgid "To disable redirects use:"
msgstr "要禁用重定向使用："

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:163
msgid "REDIRECT_ENABLED = False"
msgstr "REDIRECT_ENABLED = False"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:170
msgid "Crawl in BFO order"
msgstr "BFO 顺序中的 Crawl"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:172
msgid ":ref:`Scrapy crawls in DFO order by default <faq-bfo-dfo>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:174
msgid ""
"In broad crawls, however, page crawling tends to be faster than page "
"processing. As a result, unprocessed early requests stay in memory until the "
"final depth is reached, which can significantly increase memory usage."
msgstr ""
"然而，在广义上的胶合板上，页面的编排速度往往比页面处理速度快。 结果，未处理的"
"提早请求在达到最后深度之前保持内存，这可能大大增加内存使用率。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:178
msgid ":ref:`Crawl in BFO order <faq-bfo-dfo>` instead to save memory."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:182
msgid "Be mindful of memory leaks"
msgstr "请注意内存泄漏。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:184
msgid ""
"If your broad crawl shows a high memory usage, in addition to :ref:`crawling "
"in BFO order <broad-crawls-bfo>` and :ref:`lowering concurrency <broad-"
"crawls-concurrency>` you should :ref:`debug your memory leaks <topics-"
"leaks>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:191
msgid "Install a specific Twisted reactor"
msgstr "安装特定的扭曲反应堆。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:193
msgid ""
"If the crawl is exceeding the system's capabilities, you might want to try "
"installing a specific Twisted reactor, via the :setting:`TWISTED_REACTOR` "
"setting."
msgstr ""
